data.description: No need to wait for new construction. Do you need a home with lots of space and is well maintained? This popular 5 bedroom home with several updates is a must see. The large kitchen offers plenty of counter space and has all new (2022) stainless steel appliances, including a freestanding double oven with a center grill on the cooktop. Upgraded luxury vinyl flooring was installed in 2020, newly painted exterior and a beautiful new concrete driveway and entry walkway. The large 3 car garage is insulated, and the RV parking is ample with a gate and extensive paver work. The exterior features a lush fully landscaped front and backyard. A perfect space for entertaining on the gazebo shaded back patio or just tranquil sitting space to enjoy the mountain views under the Reno stars. There is a nice storage shed to keep all your extras protected. A few other notables, the house has a newer air purification system, the washing machine is a dual washing machine, giving you the option to do a smaller load and the upstairs bathroom shower head has a water filter. Primary bedroom is large with a huge walk in closet. Please note, some pictures of the yard are from last year's summer.
